SummaryEnglish: Once upon a time, there was an alien child in the mysterious forest. He wore a mask and was clever and weird. He was with the monkeys blowing bubbles all day long. One day, a group of extremely ferocious sark-tooth wolves rushed into the forest. They saw the cosmic elf catcher Carat sitting on the wolf, colliding with the SPT team members who were looking for the saint Pony.  A fierce battle from heaven to earth begins! Along the way, the SPT team members came across man-eating sharks, wild boars, holy brilliance butterflies, flash bibos, fang fish, mushroom monsters...  Who is the enemy? Can they successfully find Pony and start the next journey of the Purcell?
